AbilityScoreFeature.Name: Ability Score Increase
AbilityScoreFeature.Text: Your Dexterity score increases by 2 and your Constitution score increases by 1.

Feature.Name: Age
Feature.Text: Grungs mature to adulthood in a single year, but have been known to live up to 50 years.

Feature.Name: Alignment
Feature.Text: Most grungs are lawful, having been raised in a strict caste system. They tend toward evil as well, coming from a culture where social advancement occurs rarely, and most often because another member of your army has died and there is no one else of that caste to fill the vacancy.

SkillProficiencyFeature.Name: Arboreal Alertness
SkillProficiencyFeature.Text: You have proficiency in the Perception skill.

Feature.Name: Size
Feature.Text: Grungs stand between 2 ½ and 3 ½ feet tall and average about 30 pounds. Your size is Small.

SpeedFeature.Name: Speed
SpeedFeature.Text: Your base walking speed is 25 feet, and you have a climbing speed of 25 feet.

ResistanceFeature.Name: Poison Immunity
ResistanceFeature.Text: You’re immune to poison damage and the poisoned condition.

Feature.Name: Poisonous Skin
Feature.Text: Any creature that grapples you or otherwise comes into direct contact with your skin must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or become poisoned for 1 minute. A poisoned creature no longer in direct contact with you can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. You can also apply this poison to any piercing weapon as part of an attack with that weapon, though when you hit the poison reacts differently. The target must succeed on a DC 12 Constitution saving throw or take 2d4 poison damage.

Feature.Name: Standing Leap
Feature.Text: Your long jump is up to 25 feet and your high jump is up to 15 feet, with or without a running start.

Feature.Name: Water Dependency
Feature.Text: If you fail to immerse yourself in water for at least 1 hour during a day, you suffer one level of exhaustion at the end of that day. You can only recover from this exhaustion through magic or by immersing yourself in water for at least 1 hour.

LanguageProficiencyFeature.Name: Languages
LanguageProficiencyFeature.Text: You can speak, read, and write Grung

Race.Name: Grung
Race.Description: Your grung character has an assortment of inborn abilities, part and parcel of grung nature.
